Section 1:
HB1371 FA1 BolesBr-JL
3/25/2025 9:51:23 am
FLOOR AMENDMENT
HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
State of Oklahoma
SPEAKER:
CHAIR:
I move to amend HB1371
Page 7 Section 1 Lines 4 - 7
Of the Engrossed Bill
By deleting the following phrase, "payment returned to the operator as
undeliverable or the payment check is never cashed by the royalty owner,
such proceeds shall not earn interest", and by inserting in lieu thereof
the following phrase, "physical payment check was returned to the payor
operator as undeliverable or the physical payment check is never cashed by
the royalty owner, such proceeds shall not earn interest after the date
the physical payment check was mailed. The payor operator shall maintain
records of such mailing dates and copies of any undeliverable envelopes
and physical payment checks. This provision shall only apply to physical
payment checks mailed to an address provided by such royalty owner to the
payor operator".
AMEND TITLE TO CONFORM TO AMENDMENTS
Amendment submitted by: Brad Boles
Adopted: _____________________________
